<path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4C4 3.44772 4.44772 3 5 3H19C19.5523 3 20 3.44772 20 4V16H18V5H6V19H15V21H5C4.44772 21 4 20.5523 4 20V4Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path> <path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M14 20C14 20.4044 14.2436 20.7691 14.6173 20.9238C14.991 21.0786 15.4211 20.9931 15.7071 20.7071L19.7071 16.7071C19.9931 16.4211 20.0786 15.991 19.9239 15.6173C19.7691 15.2436 19.4044 15 19 15L15 15C14.7348 15 14.4804 15.1053 14.2929 15.2929C14.1053 15.4804 14 15.7348 14 16L14 20Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path> <path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8.5 7.5C7.94771 7.5 7.5 7.94772 7.5 8.5C7.5 9.05228 7.94771 9.5 8.5 9.5L15.5 9.5C16.0523 9.5 16.5 9.05228 16.5 8.5C16.5 7.94772 16.0523 7.5 15.5 7.5L8.5 7.5ZM8.5 11.5C7.94771 11.5 7.5 11.9477 7.5 12.5C7.5 13.0523 7.94771 13.5 8.5 13.5L13.5 13.5C14.0523 13.5 14.5 13.0523 14.5 12.5C14.5 11.9477 14.0523 11.5 13.5 11.5L8.5 11.5Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
</svg><a href="/realtime/china/story20240622-3963103">中国欧盟将就对华电动汽车反补贴调查案启动磋商 </a>
</div>
</section>
<p data-s="AE0GE======">欧盟说，欧盟和中国针对提高中国电动汽车关税的计划举行了“坦诚和建设性”的会谈，双方将进行进一步磋商。</p>
</article>]]></description><guid isPermaLink="false">3965350</guid><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 18:05:00 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>以防长访美 讨论加沙战争和以黎冲突</title><link>https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/world/story20240623-3965423</link><description><![CDATA[<div data-interval="false" data-ride="carousel" data-touch="true" id="carousel-article">
<div>
<a>
<div>
<img alt="" data-title="以色列国防部长加兰特星期天（6月23日）前往华盛顿，他启程前发声明称：“我们已准备好在加沙、黎巴嫩和更多地区采取任何必要的行动。”（法新社档案照片）" src="https://dss1.zbstatic1.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2024/06/23/FILES-US-ISRAEL-PALESTINIANS-CONFLICT-GALLANT-POLITICS-060744_0.jpg?2865230"/>
</div>
<div>
以色列国防部长加兰特星期天（6月23日）前往华盛顿，他启程前发声明称：“我们已准备好在加沙、黎巴嫩和更多地区采取任何必要的行动。”（法新社档案照片）
</div>
</a>
</div>
</div><article id="article-body">
<p data-s="Y0PGI======">路透社报道，加兰特星期天（6月23日）启程前往华盛顿之前发表声明称：“我们已准备好在加沙、黎巴嫩和更多地区采取任何必要的行动。”</p>
<p data-s="l53GE======">以色列国防部长加兰特前往华盛顿，讨论加沙战争的下一阶段，以及在黎巴嫩边境不断升级的敌对行动。</p>
<section data-s="3BCG4======">
<h4>
<div>
    延伸阅读
   </div></h4>
<div>
<svg fill="none" height="24" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4C4 3.44772 4.44772 3 5 3H19C19.5523 3 20 3.44772 20 4V16H18V5H6V19H15V21H5C4.44772 21 4 20.5523 4 20V4Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path> <path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M14 20C14 20.4044 14.2436 20.7691 14.6173 20.9238C14.991 21.0786 15.4211 20.9931 15.7071 20.7071L19.7071 16.7071C19.9931 16.4211 20.0786 15.991 19.9239 15.6173C19.7691 15.2436 19.4044 15 19 15L15 15C14.7348 15 14.4804 15.1053 14.2929 15.2929C14.1053 15.4804 14 15.7348 14 16L14 20Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path> <path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8.5 7.5C7.94771 7.5 7.5 7.94772 7.5 8.5C7.5 9.05228 7.94771 9.5 8.5 9.5L15.5 9.5C16.0523 9.5 16.5 9.05228 16.5 8.5C16.5 7.94772 16.0523 7.5 15.5 7.5L8.5 7.5ZM8.5 11.5C7.94771 11.5 7.5 11.9477 7.5 12.5C7.5 13.0523 7.94771 13.5 8.5 13.5L13.5 13.5C14.0523 13.5 14.5 13.0523 14.5 12.5C14.5 11.9477 14.0523 11.5 13.5 11.5L8.5 11.5Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
</svg><a href="/realtime/world/story20240620-3955040">黎巴嫩真主党向以色列发射数十枚火箭弹</a>
</div>
<div>
<svg fill="none" height="24" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4C4 3.44772 4.44772 3 5 3H19C19.5523 3 20 3.44772 20 4V16H18V5H6V19H15V21H5C4.44772 21 4 20.5523 4 20V4Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path> <path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M14 20C14 20.4044 14.2436 20.7691 14.6173 20.9238C14.991 21.0786 15.4211 20.9931 15.7071 20.7071L19.7071 16.7071C19.9931 16.4211 20.0786 15.991 19.9239 15.6173C19.7691 15.2436 19.4044 15 19 15L15 15C14.7348 15 14.4804 15.1053 14.2929 15.2929C14.1053 15.4804 14 15.7348 14 16L14 20Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path> <path clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8.5 7.5C7.94771 7.5 7.5 7.94772 7.5 8.5C7.5 9.05228 7.94771 9.5 8.5 9.5L15.5 9.5C16.0523 9.5 16.5 9.05228 16.5 8.5C16.5 7.94772 16.0523 7.5 15.5 7.5L8.5 7.5ZM8.5 11.5C7.94771 11.5 7.5 11.9477 7.5 12.5C7.5 13.0523 7.94771 13.5 8.5 13.5L13.5 13.5C14.0523 13.5 14.5 13.0523 14.5 12.5C14.5 11.9477 14.0523 11.5 13.5 11.5L8.5 11.5Z" fill="#333333" fill-rule="evenodd"></path>
</svg><a href="/realtime/world/story20240617-3936887">以色列：真主党跨境袭击加剧恐带来“毁灭性后果”</a>
</div>
</section>
<p data-s="sM8GM======">加兰特将会见美国防长奥斯汀和国务卿布林肯。</p>
<p data-s="4hZGEYQ====">自八个多月前加沙战争爆发以来，伊朗支持的黎巴嫩真主党一直与以色列交火。</p>
<script data-s="2qoGU======" type="text/javascript"> googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('dfp-ad-imu1'); }); </script>
<p data-s="BL5GY======">一些以色列官员将以色列不断向拉法推进的行动，与可能重点对付黎巴嫩联系起来。</p>
<p data-s="4lWHA======">官员们称，以色列对加沙进攻的第三阶段和最后阶段是逐步结束战争，同时加紧努力稳定局势，并开始重建加沙。</p>
<section data-s="j0BGQ======">
<div data-google-query-id="CNeNn4_J8YYDFeJtDwId4_YEkQ" id="dfp-ad-imu1"><div id="google_ads_iframe_/5908/ZB_CN/imu1/realtime/world_0__container__"></div></div>
</section>
<p data-s="hVmGEYA====">美国总统拜登的高级顾问<a href="/realtime/world/story20240618-3944021" target="_blank">霍希斯坦上周访问了以色列和黎巴嫩</a>，尝试缓解紧张局势，因为双方的跨境交火不断增加，言词也越来越激烈。</p>
<p data-s="w9DHE======">加兰特似乎在声明中也提到上述联系。“加沙过渡到C阶段非常重要。我将与美国官员讨论这个过渡，讨论可以如何实现更多目标，我们也将就此问题与美国达成密切合作。”</p>
</article>]]></description><guid isPermaLink="false">3965423</guid><pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 18:17:46 +0800</pubDate></item></channel></rss>